data.title: Starter English Read & Write Step 1
data.description: This "Starter" series book, "English: Read and Write Level 1," introduces pre-primary children to fundamental reading and writing skills. It uses engaging activities to build a strong foundation for early English language acquisition.
data.subject: English

data.title: Starter English Read & Write Step 2
data.description: Starter English: Read and Write Level 2" advances pre-primary learners' literacy within the "Starter" series. It builds on foundational skills, introducing new vocabulary and guided writing practice for developing fluency.
data.subject: English

data.title: Starter English Read & Write Step 3
data.description: This "Starter" series book, "English: Read and Write Level 3," prepares pre-primary children for more advanced literacy. It reinforces reading strategies and encourages creative writing, building confidence for the next learning stage.
data.subject: English

data.title: Starter English Count & Learn Step 1
data.description: This "Starter" series book for Nursery introduces young learners to fundamental mathematical concepts through counting and engaging activities. It builds a strong foundation for early number sense and recognition.
data.subject: Mathematics

data.title: Starter English Count & Learn Step 2
data.description: Building on Nursery concepts, this "Starter" series book for KG1 expands mathematical understanding through counting, basic operations, and engaging activities. It develops early problem-solving skills and number fluency.
data.subject: Mathematics

data.title: Starter English Count & Learn Step 3
data.description: The "Starter" series' Level 3 book for KG2 consolidates and refines mathematical skills, focusing on more complex counting, basic arithmetic, and problem-solving. It prepares children for elementary mathematics with practical application.
data.subject: Mathematics
